<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF109-452-969  </DOCNO><DOCID>09 452 969.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  July 17 1990* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Mindscape launches Toolworks label in UK. (MindscapeInternational's licenses its business software to SoftwareToolworks)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Gold, Steve.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Mindscape Inc. (contracts)Software Toolworks Inc. (contracts).andO;Ticker:    MIND; TWRX.andO;Topic:     Marketing AgreementsUnited KingdomMarketing StrategyOEMs.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>MINDSCAPE LAUNCHES TOOLWORKS LABEL IN UK HAYWARDS HEATH, ENGLAND, 1990 JUL 14(NB) -- Mindscape International has signed a licensing deal with SoftwareToolworks in the US which calls for Mindscape to market all its businesssoftware under the Toolworks label.andM;According to Geoff Heath, Mindscape International's managing director, thedeal allows Mindscape, traditionally associated with games and entertainmentsoftware, to differentiate between games and business software.andM;&quot;Now that we operate separate sales divisions for business and entertainmentproducts, each sales manager can present a much clearer picture of the tworanges, each of which has a clearly defined market position,&quot; he said.andM;(Steve Gold/199900714/Press andamp; Public Contact: Geoff Heath, MindscapeInternational, Tel: 0444-86545)</TEXT></DOC>